{"tid":568199,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到芬蘭教育，覺得香港學生真係好撚慘","createTime":"2018-02-21T14:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T14:52:13.000Z","uid":40525,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10e1fe9f6bd0447636ce9361c0a49534f61b9aea","tid":568199,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"香港學生：<br />\n死CHUR，通頂，無自由<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭學生：<br />\n遲入學、教得少，教得慢、少功課、不操練、不重分數、只得一個公開試的教育體制，學生看似玩多過學的國度，如何仍能在國際評核中取得不錯的成績。<br />\n<br />\n課堂不講求教得多、教得快、教學內容豐富，而是要孩子學得懂，容讓每位學生有選擇、自主學習、自由發揮，讓他們學會欣賞自己卻是真實的。學校對孩子的期望，正如Koulumesteri學校的校長所說：「每個孩子都有他們的強項，我希望他們會覺得自己是重要的人，能在社會上找到立足之處。」<br />\n<br />\n其實呢種教育法真係好正<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2BHxQEz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BHxQEz&d=n5f1urfBbF4NdF4zZ9erVZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=9cf1eb74\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2BHxQEz</a>"},{"pid":"ca1a760a9176bc6d14fa18e6a5f6722fc022f11c","tid":568199,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"華人社會都鍾意填鴨式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad78d9f229038b00174d29a5fac6c9075be5485","tid":568199,"uid":30821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"希望下世投胎喺歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336d14163ce21dcd1bba8b6f3a5a5628ecb32ebb","tid":568199,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"有冇移民plan"},{"pid":"096758387679b64d0ef3e192226c924ff94db53e","tid":568199,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca1a760a9176bc6d14fa18e6a5f6722fc022f11c","tid":568199,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"華人社會都鍾意填鴨式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"真，操練，鳩背<br />\n家長太撚要面，過度催谷小朋友"},{"pid":"2bcf72